data.description: Discover effortless one-story living in this delightful rambler in Ponderosa Estates! Cozy up by the fireplace on cool nights and beat the heat in the summers with central A/C. Prepare meals in style and entertain with ease in this light-filled kitchen that also boasts stainless steel appliances. The serene primary bedroom offers dual closets plus an ensuite bathroom to unwind in comfort and style. Enjoy the covered front porch and added peace of mind with a fully fenced yard. Plus, with extra parking available, inviting guests over or accommodating your RV or boat is a breeze. Conveniently located close to shopping and restaurants, indulge in the vibrant amenities of the area while relishing the ease and comfort of your new home!
